features: Quickly identify luggage with builtin ID card slot
Durable design comprised of a solid exoskeleton, reinforcing bumpers, wear-resistant material, wear rails and oversized YKK zippers
Organize and separate personal gear in two large packing areas of the divided main compartment
Expand luggage 2.5" for additional packing space
Belongings are held securely in place with internal compression wings with zippered storage pockets
Exceptional stability and a smooth, steady pull from the patented V-tubing telescoping handle and wide wheel base
Comfortably lift and arrange luggage with retractable top, side and bottom grab handles
Easily access go-to items using two front panel pockets with ample storage and a mesh divider for organization
Easily navigate from doorstep to destination with oversized rear wheels that easily glide over rough terrain and smaller, recessed front wheels that increase interior space
Prevent unauthorized access and keep contents safe with a TSA lock
